{"tid":1392174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水炮車弱點(發夢)","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:38:21.000Z","uid":49522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6f30c4924c80d2d999b3e53d1e1b9b50226e34","tid":1392174,"uid":49522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"呢排成日都發緊同一個夢 俾水炮車打<br />\n諗緊點算好<br />\n<br />\n遊擊當然係最好 但係咁多人點一齊遊<br />\n要分team 有組織先做到個效果<br />\n當日出到去好大機會又係守<br />\n<br />\n水炮車擋吾擋到？暫時未有方法爆車胎 擋住水衝擊<br />\n<br />\n咁剩返落黎我地優勢係咩？就係簡戰場!<br />\n<br />\n人多地方好似旺角呢d好多市民 萬一佢射錯就大檸樂 有機會就住就住射 就算佢吾就住 射錯佢都係出事<br />\n<br />\n你去金鐘呢d無咩市民地方就只有攬炒 擋水炮車姿勢係要訓係地下保護頭部先減少衝擊 內臟無咁易受傷 但係就訓低等俾人拉 所以有得跑好跑 <br />\n<br />\n今晚吾好又發呢d惡夢就好"},{"pid":"c03575c86b1235aca7a9785e0908c48ca490f0ff","tid":1392174,"uid":5499,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"水炮車弱點係廣東道名店，你賠唔賠得起呀，死黑警"},{"pid":"11e5f857e773c07651afeb7ec985a87b38895fb1","tid":1392174,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"560790de0982647d08ec80d801c9016e3791ab11","tid":1392174,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"be water"},{"pid":"1f5163642504cd37b26476e6643c9deafd06db3f","tid":1392174,"uid":271962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"一個字：走!<br />\n水砲點擋呀, 就只可以打游擊"},{"pid":"da76998dab55ed9be541aec18c55851af5c6c658","tid":1392174,"uid":271962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"借位, 求留毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1391553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1391553</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8.5 三大罷 七區集會</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"